    WebHandler, org.apache.flink.shaded.netty4.io.netty.channel.ChannelHandler, org.apache.flink.shaded.netty4.io.netty.channel.ChannelInboundHandler

    @ChannelHandler.Sharable
public class TaskManagerLogHandler
extends RedirectHandler<JobManagerGateway>
implements WebHandler
    Request handler that returns the TaskManager log/out files.

    This code is based on the "HttpStaticFileServerHandler" from the Netty project's HTTP server example.
